original_title: The Few, the Proud, the Naked! 14
overview: Military master Dirk Yates gets his "cream of the crop" Marines together and interviews these studly jarheads in this extremely popular solo video series. Featuring big-dicked Private Sean Summers, it's all real Marines showing off the best way they've got. Often imitated... but never duplicated.
title: The Few, the Proud, the Naked! 14
